# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-06-02 11:43

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:9
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_d6193e41:

    # "Feeling this strange tug, almost like Reba is calling, I walk down the path towards her."
    "Sentindo este estranho puxão, quase como se a Reba estivesse a chamar, caminho pelo trilho na direção dela."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:12
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_a4fdb6df:

    # "After a while of walking, I wonder if I imagined the feeling."
    "Depois de algum tempo a caminhar, pergunto-me se terei imaginado a sensação."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:13
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_5a44d5e1:

    # "There is no indication that this is the right way at all, and no reason to think that Reba would be here."
    "Não há qualquer indício de que este seja o caminho certo, nem razão para pensar que a Reba estaria aqui."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:16
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_c423963c:

    # "Then I hear voices coming from up ahead. Yelling and weapons clanging together."
    "Então ouço vozes vindas da frente. Gritos e o barulho de armas a chocarem-se."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:20
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_69a4fcdd:

    # "I run down the path towards the noise and am surprised to see Reba in a clearing ahead, with three men surrounding her."
    "Corro pelo caminho em direção ao barulho e fico surpreendida ao ver a Reba numa clareira à frente, com três homens a cercá-la."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:23
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_aed8dec2:

    # rb "I told you buttswogglers that if you tried to touch me I'd bash your heads in!"
    rb "Eu disse-vos, seus idiotas, que se tentassem tocar-me, eu esmagava-vos a cabeça!"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:24
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_a5b2fc7b:

    # rb "Now leave me alone!"
    rb "Agora deixem-me em paz!"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:25
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_7805dc36:

    # "Bandit 1" "Oh, I don't think so, lovely. Now you got us mad."
    "Bandit 1" "Oh, acho que não, querida. Agora deixaste-nos furiosos."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:26
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_09e8e2db:

    # "Bandit 2" "You might be able to take one of us, but not all three. Not by your lonesome."
    "Bandit 2" "Talvez consigas dar conta de um de nós, mas não dos três. Não sozinha."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:29
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_8248f701:

    # "I pull my sword out of its sheath, holding it in front of me as confidently as I can."
    "Tiro a minha espada da bainha, segurando-a à minha frente com toda a confiança que consigo."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:30
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_ee0a4ba4:

    # pc "She's not alone! Get away from her, you... buttswogglers."
    pc "Ela não está sozinha! Afastem-se dela, seus... idiotas."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:33
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_01d3ae6b:

    # "Bandit 1" "You picked the wrong fight, boy. Should've just kept walking."
    "Bandit 1" "Escolheste a briga errada, rapaz. Devias ter continuado a andar."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:34
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_aec1c970:

    # "Bandit 2" "Now we gotta kill you both!"
    "Bandit 2" "Agora temos de matar-vos aos dois!"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:37
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_484e806e:

    # "I hear Reba screaming in fury, but my focus is on the guy with the sword charging right at me now."
    "Ouço a Reba a gritar furiosa, mas o meu foco está no tipo com a espada que está a atacar-me agora."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:38
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_9b2b4b2a:

    # "I try my best to block with my sword, but I don't know what the fuck I'm doing."
    "Faço o meu melhor para bloquear com a minha espada, mas não sei o que raio estou a fazer."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:41
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_81fc296b:

    # "I've seen sword fighting in movies and stuff, but this is different. It's messier."
    "Já vi lutas de espadas em filmes e tal, mas isto é diferente. É mais confuso."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:42
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_50d85c84:

    # "Our weapons smash into each other, but they keep going, his blade sliding dangerously close to my hands and arms."
    "As nossas armas chocam uma contra a outra, mas continuam a avançar, a lâmina dele a deslizar perigosamente perto das minhas mãos e braços."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:45
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_011dca34:

    # "Then I trip over a root, falling backwards."
    "Depois tropeço numa raiz, caindo de costas."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:46
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_9b11d9fe:

    # "I lose my grip and the sword flies from my hands and clatters across the ground."
    "Perco o equilíbrio e a espada voa das minhas mãos e bate no chão com estrondo."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:49
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_f2b252a6:

    # "Bandit 1" "Bad news, boy: you're not very good at swordfighting."
    "Bandit 1" "Más notícias, rapaz: não és muito bom a lutar com espadas."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:50
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_d5514087:

    # "Bandit 1" "Time to die."
    "Bandit 1" "Está na hora de morrer."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:51
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_3b1d2205:

    # pc "No, wait!"
    pc "Não, espera!"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:54
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_003839a3:

    # "Then Reba smashes her club into the side of the man's head, caving it in and dropping him like a marionette whose strings have been cut."
    "Então a Reba esmaga o seu bastão na lateral da cabeça do homem, afundando-a e derrubando-o como uma marioneta cujos fios foram cortados."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:57
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_72b62d77:

    # "Once he's on the ground, she slams her club into him a couple more times for good measure."
    "Assim que ele está no chão, ela esmaga-lhe o bastão mais umas vezes, por precaução."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:59
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_98c8d795:

    # rb "I warned you!"
    rb "Eu avisei-te!"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:61
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_f68be640:

    # rb "I tole you to stay away from me!"
    rb "Eu disse-te para te afastares de mim!"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:63
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_cc15a689:

    # rb "STUPID!"
    rb "ESTÚPIDOS!"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:65
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_d3cf4267:

    # rb "DUMB!"
    rb "IDIOTAS!"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:67
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_d7a4e723:

    # rb "JERKS!"
    rb "IMBÉCILES!"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:70
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_1f493a2c:

    # rb "RAAAAAAAAAAAHHHHHHHHHH!"
    rb "RAAAAAAAAAAAHHHHHHHHHH!"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:71
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_ff50a7ed:

    # "I back away a bit on the ground, hoping that she doesn't come after me next."
    "Recuo um pouco no chão, na esperança de que ela não venha atrás de mim a seguir."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:74
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_ab0cc730:

    # "Then she looks at me, like she had almost forgotten I was here."
    "Então ela olha para mim, como se quase se tivesse esquecido que eu estava aqui."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:75
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_77773a08:

    # rb "Dang! That sucked! I hate when people get me like that."
    rb "Raios! Isso foi horrível! Detesto quando as pessoas me fazem isto."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:76
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_e09cad3f:

    # rb "Are you okay?"
    rb "Estás bem?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:77
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_bed2a4be:

    # pc "Uh... yeah, I think so. Are you?"
    pc "Uh... sim, acho que sim. E tu?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:80
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_883c8415:

    # rb "Yeah. They were trying to touch me, but I didn't let them."
    rb "Sim. Estavam a tentar tocar-me, mas não os deixei."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:81
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_fe7a3737:

    # pc "Are you Reba?"
    pc "És a Reba?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:82
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_8e53d88d:

    # rb "Yeah. How'd you know my name? Do we know each other?"
    rb "Sim. Como é que sabes o meu nome? Nós conhecemo-nos?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:85
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_9be282fb:

    # pc "Sort of. It's hard to explain. I'm from a different world, where there is another version of you."
    pc "Mais ou menos. É difícil de explicar. Sou de um mundo diferente, onde existe outra versão de ti."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:86
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_8d1a1ea3:

    # rb "Another me?"
    rb "Outra eu?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:87
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_c5e041c4:

    # pc "Yeah. I know, it doesn't make any sense."
    pc "Sim. Eu sei, não faz sentido nenhum."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:88
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_77d587c6:

    # rb "That's okay. I seen a lot of things I don't understand. Magic and whatnot."
    rb "Não faz mal. Já vi muitas coisas que não compreendo. Magia e coisas do género."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:91
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_88c8b170:

    # rb "I ain't gotta understand it to know that it's true."
    rb "Não preciso de compreender para saber que é verdade."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:92
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_494dcb66:

    # rb "I feel something between us. I feel like I know you. That's good enough for me."
    rb "Sinto algo entre nós. Sinto que te conheço. Para mim, isso basta."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:93
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_8fe5bf65:

    # rb "Plus, you saved me from those dummies."
    rb "Além disso, salvaste-me daqueles idiotas."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:96
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_1fc43ebb:

    # pc "I don't think I did much."
    pc "Acho que não fiz grande coisa."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:97
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_3a80bf2f:

    # rb "Yeah, you were pretty lame in the fight, but you distracted them enough that I stood a chance."
    rb "Sim, foste bastante fraco na luta, mas distraí-los o suficiente para eu ter uma hipótese."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:98
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_6ed0b2ec:

    # rb "I think if I had to take all three, they might have gotten a swing on me. I'm glad to not be injured."
    rb "Acho que se tivesse de enfrentar os três, eles poderiam ter-me acertado. Estou contente por não estar ferido."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:99
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_89bf9b0f:

    # rb "So where are you heading?"
    rb "Então, para onde vais?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:102
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_cab5ada1:

    # pc "North. To the Ice Queen's castle."
    pc "Para norte. Para o castelo da Rainha do Gelo."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:103
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_22920754:

    # rb "That's where I'm heading too! We can travel together!"
    rb "É para lá que eu também vou! Podemos viajar juntos!"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:104
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_4f1735dd:

    # pc "Sounds good to me."
    pc "Por mim, tudo bem."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:107
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_f2118212:

    # pc "Why are you going to the Ice Queen?"
    pc "Porque vais ter com a Rainha do Gelo?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:108
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_54e10752:

    # rb "Lookin' for my brother. Dumbass went to join up with her army. Gonna try to talk some sense into him."
    rb "À procura do meu irmão. O idiota foi juntar-se ao exército dela. Vou tentar fazê-lo entrar em razão."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:109
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_9b21e861:

    # rb "Anyway, we better get going. And I have to clean off all this dang blood."
    rb "De qualquer forma, é melhor irmos. E eu tenho de limpar todo este raio de sangue."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:112
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_da4050d7:

    # "Reba and I continue down the path north, together now."
    "A Reba e eu continuamos a seguir pelo caminho para norte, agora juntos."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:113
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_53503d71:

    # "I'm still nervous about all of this, especially after that fight, but it's nice to have somebody with me."
    "Ainda estou nervoso com tudo isto, especialmente depois daquela luta, mas é bom ter alguém comigo."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:114
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_4fb601c4:

    # rb "Gonna have to teach you how to fight a bit. That was embarrassing."
    rb "Vou ter de te ensinar a lutar um pouco. Aquilo foi embaraçoso."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1b.rpy:115
translate portuguese u19a2s1b_95d16ca5:

    # pc "Yeah, good plan."
    pc "Sim, boa ideia."

